description: Pure Global Cannabis Inc. produces cannabis products for the medical and adult-use markets in Canada. The company provides cannabis products, such as dried flower, cannabis oils, soft gels and capsules, seedlings and clones, vape pen cartridges, topicals, sublingual strip/spray, transdermal patch, and edibles and beverages, as well as wellness products. It offers its products under the PureSinse, SPARK Medical Cannabis clinics, and The Great Canadian Hemp Company brands. The company serves medical, pharmaceutical, wellness, health and beauty, natural health, food and beverage, and recreational legal markets. Pure Global Cannabis Inc. is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
